column5: Have a good one, Paul. You have my permission to do whatever Joey wants you to do for the entire weekend.
All the best Paul, have a great day !!
Happy BDAY Bud. Have a great day.
Happy bday Paul. I hope you get out fishing to celebrate.

Thank you.  .A tear of joy swell from the corner of  the eye placing it's self  on a weathered cheek. The thought of the years that have past.Some with dark shadows.Other with great victories. Most though, carving out a living. For on this day I have became 50 of year. For the joy is not for that. It's one more year I can tell the devil to kiss my a$$.
And for your BD...I hope it is to go fishing...All the best...
Happy Birthday Paul.Have a good one!
Well Hey there Paul - Happy Birthday to ya. Hope your better half was listening to your wish list while we were up at Lakair this year. (Hint Hint)  Have a great day bud.
Happy Birthday Paul!!  Hope you are having a great day.
Happy B-day Paul! Keep yer motor, no strike that, engine running bud! HH
Happy Birthday Hon!!!  Now where did I put that present?????  Love ya babe!!  Lots of cake and candles tonight!
Woot Woot!! Happy birthday Paul !!! Fifty was great.  Can't wait to do it again
Best of the day to you Paul I hope you have a great time.  Art
